<p>

<b>Ellen Holly</b> (born <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../022/16022.xml">
January 16</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../608/34608.xml">
1931</link>) is an <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../229/99229.xml">
African</link> â€“ <body wordnetid="107965085" confidence="0.8">
